# work
#######################################################################################
IMAPAccount work
Host            outlook.office365.com
User            egallois@talend.com
PassCmd         "pass Work/Okta/password"
SSLType         IMAPS
SSLVersion      TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore work-remote
Account work

MaildirStore work-local
Path       ~/.mail/work/
Inbox      ~/.mail/work/Inbox
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel work
Master    :work-remote:
Slave     :work-local:
Patterns  * !"Conversation History" !Outbox !Notes !Contacts !Journal !Tasks
Create    Both
Expunge   Both
SyncState *
